{
  "uid": "lab-grpc",
  "title": "gRPC \u2014 Service Communication",
  "description": "The internal Order \u2192 Inventory hop: RED metrics, the client/server duration gap, and the saturation signals HTTP does not have. The last row is the one that justifies running both protocols \u2014 the same logical operation, measured side by side. See docs/Grpc.md.",
  "tags": [
    "observability-lab",
    "grpc"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": false,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "label": "Store",
        "description": "Prometheus holds 24h and evaluates the alerts; VictoriaMetrics holds the same samples for 30d. Both answer PromQL.",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prometheus"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "service",
        "label": "Service",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "${datasource}"
        },
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(up, service)",
          "refId": "service"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 100,
      "title": "Headline",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Call rate",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(grpc_server_requests_total{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])) or vector(0)",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "none",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Fault ratio",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 1
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "(sum(rate(grpc_server_requests_total{service=~\"$service\",grpc_status=~\"INTERNAL|UNKNOWN|DATA_LOSS|UNAVAILABLE\"}[$__rate_interval])) or vector(0)) / clamp_min(sum(rate(grpc_server_requests_total{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])), 0.001)",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.01
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.05
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Faults only. NOT_FOUND for an untracked SKU and FAILED_PRECONDITION for a shortage are answers, not failures \u2014 counting them would make this track catalogue quality instead of service health, and the alert built on it would be one people mute."
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 3,
      "title": "p99 (server)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 1
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(grpc_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.25
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.5
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Handling time only, excluding network. Compare with the client panel below: the difference between the two is the whole point."
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Active calls",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 1
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(grpc_server_active_calls{service=~\"$service\"}) or vector(0)",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "none",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "In flight. Rising while throughput stays flat means calls are taking longer."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 101,
      "title": "RED",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Rate by method",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (grpc_method) (rate(grpc_server_requests_total{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{grpc_method}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 8,
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          },
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Status distribution",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (grpc_status) (rate(grpc_server_requests_total{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{grpc_status}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 8,
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          },
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "OK"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "NOT_FOUND"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "FAILED_PRECONDITION"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "ALREADY_EXISTS"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "INVALID_ARGUMENT"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "PERMISSION_DENIED"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "UNAUTHENTICATED"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "DEADLINE_EXCEEDED"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "UNAVAILABLE"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "red"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "INTERNAL"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "red"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "UNKNOWN"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "red"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": "The taxonomy HTTP cannot express. Business statuses are green because they are the system working; only genuine faults are red."
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Latency percentiles (server)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(grpc_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(grpc_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(grpc_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 0,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 8,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "From bucket counts, which is the only form that aggregates across instances. The deadline is a hard boundary, so watching the bucket just below it is how a timeout is seen coming before it starts firing."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 102,
      "title": "Client versus server \u2014 the gap is the network",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 14
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 8,
      "title": "p99: what the caller waited vs what the callee spent",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(grpc_client_request_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "client p99"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(grpc_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "server p99"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 0,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 8,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "client p99"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "server p99"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "blue"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": "Both numbers are needed and they are different. The gap is transport, queueing and connection establishment: a client p99 of 400ms against a server p99 of 15ms is not a slow service, it is a saturated channel \u2014 and only having both distinguishes them. Legitimately one axis: same unit."
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 9,
      "title": "Channel state",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 15
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (state) (grpc_client_channel_state) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "{{state}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 8,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "READY"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "IDLE"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "blue"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "CONNECTING"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "TRANSIENT_FAILURE"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "red"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "SHUTDOWN"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "red"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": "TRANSIENT_FAILURE means the caller cannot reach the provider at all. It is the first thing to check when the client reports UNAVAILABLE while the provider's own dashboards are green."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 103,
      "title": "Saturation \u2014 the signals HTTP does not have",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 23
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 10,
      "title": "gRPC executor pool",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 24
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "executor_active_threads{name=\"grpc-executor\",service=~\"$service\"}",
          "legendFormat": "active"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "executor_pool_max_threads{name=\"grpc-executor\",service=~\"$service\"}",
          "legendFormat": "max"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "executor_queued_tasks{name=\"grpc-executor\",service=~\"$service\"}",
          "legendFormat": "queued"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 0,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 8,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "max"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "text"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "queued"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": "The most important panel here, and the failure with no other symptom: calls are slow, CPU is low, heap is healthy and Tomcat's pool is empty \u2014 because gRPC dispatches onto its own executor and the queue is in front of a pool nothing else measures."
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 11,
      "title": "Active calls by type",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 24
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (grpc_type) (grpc_server_active_calls{service=~\"$service\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "{{grpc_type}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "pointSize": 8,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "A SERVER_STREAMING count is the number of held subscriptions. They leak silently when a client goes away without cancelling cleanly, so a figure that only ever climbs is the signal."
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "id": 12,
      "title": "Database pool pressure",
