      "description": "The only panel in this system that deliberately puts two protocols on one axis \u2014 legitimate because they share a unit and comparison is the entire purpose. Drive it with POST /api/v1/orders/availability?transport=REST and ?transport=GRPC against the same basket. The gap widens with basket size: REST costs one round trip per line, gRPC costs one in total."
